        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1425356497" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3593322308816301285">I never really knew what evolution is till I read this book. Dawkins is great at explaining difficult concepts - making things as simple as possible, but no simpler. And his love and commitment for science is shown through his freely flowing, almost musical, prose. I loved this book. It has expanded my horizons.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


